pyStim 0.0.2
2013-08-14
=======

Python script for automated stimulus sequence calculation. Contains sub-routines for stimulus presentation paradigms (currently only “harari”).

Currently selects non-identical files per trial in a random guessing manner until the criteria are validated. A convergent algorythm may be implemented in future versions.

DEPENDS on:
numpy
pandas

Released under the GPLv3 license.
Project led by Horea Christian (address all correspondence to: h.chr@mail.ru)
